     C                     SETOF                     OF
     C                     END
     C                     EXCPTME
      ******
      ******
     CL1                   EXSR SUB2
     CL1                   EXCPTGK1
     CLR                   EXSR SUB1
     CLR                   EXCPTGK2
      ****************
      * ＳＵＢ－１ *
      ****************
     C           SUB1      BEGSR
      * 停止時間Ａ *
     C                     Z-ADD0         DAMI1   50
