     C           TISC1     DIV  TISD1     TISE1  105
     C           TISC1     DIV  TISD1     YY1     84H
     C                     END
     C           YY1       MULT 100       GR15    52
      * 設備総合効率 *
     C           TISE1     MULT ZZ1       ZZ2     94H
     C           ZZ2       MULT 100       GR16    52
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         KITN1
     C                     ENDSR
      ****************
      * ＳＵＢ－２ *
      ****************
