      * 稼動時間－Ｂ *
     C           GK10      SUB  TISB1     TISD1
      * 性能稼動率 *
     C           TISC1     IFEQ 0
     C                     Z-ADD0         ZZ1
     C                     ELSE
     C           KITN2     DIV  TISC1     ZZ1       H
     C                     END
     C           ZZ1       MULT 100       GK14    52
      * 時間稼動率 *
     C           TISD1     IFEQ 0
